es.jrq.pcc.core.service

Class RoyaltyManagerService

  • java.lang.Object
    • es.jrq.pcc.core.service.RoyaltyManagerService

  • public final class RoyaltyManagerService
extends java.lang.Object
    Royalty Manager Service. Main Back-end implementation of Royalty Manager Service providing: - Singleton instance of the class. - Service layer Interface methods to interact with configured Data Source DAO access is encapsulated in this class and is not accessible outside this framework
    Author:
    JRQ
